          <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.65;color:#52617A;margin:0">Third-party access only happens when you explicitly grant permission — scoped per application to exactly what it needs. An accounting integration like Xero only reaches the documents relevant to that workflow. Nothing more.</p>
