            <div style="display:flex;gap:13px"><span style="color:#1F8A5B;font-weight:800;flex-shrink:0;font-size:17px">&#10003;</span><div><b style="font-weight:700;color:#083A4D">Visible and deliberate</b><span style="color:#52617A"> — your team knows exactly which applications have access and why.</span></div></div>
            <div style="display:flex;gap:13px"><span style="color:#1F8A5B;font-weight:800;flex-shrink:0;font-size:17px">&#10003;</span><div><b style="font-weight:700;color:#083A4D">Reviewable and revocable</b><span style="color:#52617A"> — review or revoke any permission at any time.</span></div></div>
          </div>
          <div style="margin-top:24px;padding-top:22px;border-top:1px solid #ECE5D8;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;color:#7A8AA0">Only connect applications you trust. Doc&#8209;Salvage gives you the controls to make that decision carefully — and to change it whenever you need to.</div>
        </div>
